# Backend

- NestJS modules only — one module per domain.
- No raw SQL — Prisma only via repositories.
- Validate DTOs with class-validator; share Zod schemas from packages/types.
- Event-driven: emit domain events for cross-module side effects.
- Queue long tasks via BullMQ — return 202 + job ID.
- API versioning: prefix `/api/v1`.
- Swagger documentation on all endpoints.
- Structured logging with pino — no console.log in production code.
- Auth: Clerk JWT guard on protected routes.
